Directory listing:

ATAC:

BAM deduplication:
bam_dedup.py (using read/mate start positions only)
bam_dedup_4ends.py (using read/mate start/CIGAR)
bam_dedup_stats.py
concat_bam.py

Make fragment files:
make_fragments.py

MACS2 peaks:
MACS2_callpeaks.py (starting from BAM file)
MACS2_callpeaks_macsPE.py (starting from BEDPE file)
maxSubPeak.py
peak_iterative_overlap.py
extendPeaks.py
plusMinus_bed.py
compareBED.py

Cell quality control:
cellQC_files.py
CB_counts.py (BAM input file)
cellQC_stats.R
cellQC_filter.R
cellQC_postQC_peak_inputs.py
cellQC_postQC_files.py
getTabix.py
CB_counts_fragments.R (fragment input file)
ArchR_doublets.R

Peaks x cells matrices:
peaks_by_cells.R
concat_matrices.R


mRNA:

Cell quality control:
mRNA_fromCRarc_cellQCfilters.R
mRNA_scrublet.py
mRNA_addScrubletToMeta.R


Note:
All scripts have script and input descriptions with python or Rscript -h

